        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6 text-gray-900">Get started in minutes, not hours.</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          Unlike other Linux setup scripts that overwhelm you with technical jargon, OmniSet asks just a few simple
          questions about how you plan to use your computer. Then it handles all the complex stuff behind the scenes.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          Your time is valuable. Instead of spending hours researching package managers and configuration files,
          answer a few quick questions and let OmniSet set up your perfect environment while you grab a coffee.
        </p>
